headline: Campbell’s Named to Civic 50 Greater Philadelphia in Recognition of Community Impact Work
summary: CAMDEN, N.J., June 27, 2025--The Campbell's Company (NASDAQ:CPB ) has been named a 2025 honoree of the Civic 50 Greater Philadelphia by the Chamber of Commerce for Greater Philadelphia in partnership with the nonprofit Points of Light.
